data.description: Sitting just one block off of Texas Ave,  on a large corner lot. Neat, clean and spacious Bridge City home. This home features 4 bedrooms 2 full baths and a 5th bedroom or a game-room. Large spacious kitchen with island and breakfast bar, open to a dining area. The living room is spacious with a wood burning fireplace. Large mud room, and two work shops. Close to shopping, schools.
